Install un WINDOWS
=================

NodeJs
------
Download and install: https://nodejs.org/en/download/

Arduino
-------
Windows driver: https://www.arduino.cc/en/Main/Software

XP problemu gadijuma instrukcija: http://woodsgood.ca/projects/2014/11/18/driver-for-arduino-nano-with-ch340g-usb-chip/, kur, japalaiž http://www.wch.cn/download/CH341SER_EXE.html

NODE
--
Janokope https://github.com/uldisn/arduino_rs232_http

Direktorija  arduino_rs232_http japalaiž:

    ```
    npm install
    ```
Kas sainstales visas nepiecieshamas NodeJs bibliotekas.

config.ini faila jauzliek korektais COM ports, kam pieslegts ARDUINO un jauzrada, sensoram izmantotais bits.

Šaja piemera 4 sensors pieslegts 2 Arduino bitam:
    ```
    [sensor_4]
    bit=2
    ```    
    
No komandrindas programmu palaiž:

    ```
    node collect.js
    ```
    
Var izmantot ar parametriem:
    
    ```
    node collect.js [config.ini] [debug]
    ```
Kur:

config.ini - kofig fails
debug - rada papildus info

Palaist ka servisu
==================

NodeJs palaisanai, ka servisu  izmanto - the Non-Sucking Service Manager
https://www.nssm.cc/download

Japalaizj:

  ```
  nssm install
  ```
  
Jauzdod setingi:

* Path - C:\Program Files\nodejs\node.exe
* Startup directory - arduino_rs232_http direktorijs
* Arguments - collect.js
* Service name: arduino_rs232_http
* Display name: Arduino RS232 HTTP
* Log on; local system account
* I/O - Output: logfails
* I/O - Error: errorfails

Kad gatavs, Task Manageri japaradas pservisam.

